stateDiagram-v2
    %% Figure 5.5 — Leave Request Lifecycle
    
    [*] --> Pending : Employee submits leave request
    
    state Pending {
        [*] --> AwaitingApproval
        AwaitingApproval --> Validated : Check BD Leave Balance (Casual, Sick, Earned)
    }
    
    Pending --> Approved : Manager / HR approves
    Pending --> Rejected : Manager / HR rejects (or Insufficient Balance)
    
    Approved --> [*] : Leave days deducted from balance bucket
    Rejected --> [*] : Request closed, no deduction
    
    note right of Pending
        Requires validation against
        Bangladesh Labour Act quotas.
    end note
